{"tid":1681290,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁天琦：香港一日有呢本基本法 我嘅政治權利都會被剝奪","createTime":"2019-10-29T10:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T11:39:43.000Z","uid":273176,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"154d58af88aca5082eff2b03823b5fa8c6080281","tid":1681290,"uid":273176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ya56MykUBVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYa56MykUBVs&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=c369fbca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ya56MykUBVs</a><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦：香港一日有呢本<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">基本法</span></strong>，一日佢都可以話我唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真心</span>擁護基本法，即係話我嘅政治權利、我嘅被選舉權一日都會被剝奪。<br />\n<br />\n唔支持香港獨立，就係唔支持五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n當今日gif都可以被DQ，天琦出到嚟唔通會可以唔被港共DQ選到議員？<br />\n有DQ嘅選舉，永遠都唔係雙普選，永遠都唔會達到五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n天琦話當獨裁成為事實，時代革命就係義務<br />\n時代革命就係香港獨立！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/13662003_10154253617061422_2210937872931552328_o_FmndJ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F13662003_10154253617061422_2210937872931552328_o_FmndJ_1200x0.png&h=c85a2a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2016/08/07/166875/i_383x255_033410405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2016%2F08%2F07%2F166875%2Fi_383x255_033410405.jpg&h=a652c2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔理你話今次運動唔講得定咩<br />\n就算今次有雙普選 <br />\n支那都可以隨時收返<br />\n做人做狗自己諗"},{"pid":"9c2595c2b46ef0ede2d506c2ea4d2264c1e9b54b","tid":1681290,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdb595a3d